data.description: This 3-bed, 1.5-bath home is a true gem that offers a harmonious blend of modern amenities and serene outdoor spaces. With a large fenced-in backyard, mature trees, attached garage with carport, full basement, new roof, and new HVAC, this home presents a wonderful opportunity to embrace a lifestyle of comfort and relaxation. Don't miss your chance to make this beautiful property your own and experience the joys of homeownership in this welcoming community. Seller is graciously offering a home warranty for the buyer's first year! Come and discover your future here!
